The paper deals with the behavior and structure of neural networks, which is a topic that falls under the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural networks (cs.NE), and cryptography and security (cs.CR). However, since the paper focuses on the evaluation and analysis of trained models, the most likely sub-categories are cs.LG and cs.CV, followed by cs.AI, cs.NE, and cs.CR.
